Class CoberturaPublisher.DescriptorImpl

    @Extension
 @Symbol(value="cobertura")
public static final class CoberturaPublisher.DescriptorImpl
extends hudson.tasks.BuildStepDescriptor<hudson.tasks.Publisher>
    Descriptor for CoberturaPublisher. Used as a singleton. The class is marked as public so that it can be accessed from views. See views/hudson/plugins/cobertura/CoberturaPublisher/*.jelly for the actual HTML fragment for the configuration screen.
